    tmp = wp.cos(v1)
    v1 = (v1 * wp.exp((tmp + 0.29 + v2 + 0.80)))
    v0 = (tmp - 0.87)
    tmp = wp.exp((0.01 - (v0 + 0.74 + v1 + 1.00)))
    v1 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.53 - v0 + 0.70)) * ((v2 + 0.70 * tmp + 0.30) - (tmp + 0.73 / v0 + 0.50)))
    v1 = 0.41
